### OS ###
.DS_Store

dist/
# pkg/web/ui/dist/ is a deliberate exception: it's the built conduit-ui SPA,
# embedded via go:embed (pkg/web/ui) and committed so the binary is
# reproducible without a Node toolchain at conduit build time. Reproduce it
# with `make ui` (see the Makefile target's comment for the pinned commit).
!pkg/web/ui/dist/
!pkg/web/ui/dist/**

